{"text_id":63616,"tokens":["We"," investigate"," the"," problem"," of"," non","-","cooperative"," scheduling"," of"," multiple"," bag","-","of","-","task"," applications"," in"," a"," distributed"," computing"," system","."," In"," this"," setting",","," each"," application"," is"," comprised"," of"," multiple"," independent"," tasks",","," and"," the"," goal"," is"," to"," minimize"," the"," total"," makes","pan"," of"," all"," applications","."," Since"," the"," applications"," are"," non","-","cooperative",","," each"," application"," is"," self","-","interested"," and"," aims"," to"," minimize"," its"," own"," makes","pan"," without"," considering"," the"," others","."," We"," propose"," a"," novel"," scheduling"," framework"," that"," utilizes"," game"," theory"," to"," model"," the"," strategic"," interactions"," among"," the"," applications","."," Specifically",","," we"," formulate"," the"," problem"," as"," a"," non","-","cooperative"," game",","," where"," each"," application"," is"," a"," player"," that"," competes"," for"," resources"," to"," minimize"," its"," own"," makes","pan","."," We"," then"," develop"," a"," distributed"," scheduling"," algorithm"," based"," on"," the"," Nash"," equilibrium"," concept",","," which"," enables"," the"," applications"," to"," converge"," to"," a"," stable"," scheduling"," solution","."," Our"," experimental"," results"," show"," that"," the"," proposed"," algorithm"," achieves"," significant"," improvements"," in"," terms"," of"," total"," makes","pan"," and"," fairness"," compared"," to"," existing"," scheduling"," approaches","."," The"," motivation"," for"," this"," research"," is"," to"," provide"," an"," efficient"," and"," fair"," scheduling"," mechanism"," for"," distributed"," computing"," systems",","," where"," multiple"," applications"," compete"," for"," shared"," resources","."," By"," addressing"," the"," non","-","cooperative"," scheduling"," problem",","," we"," aim"," to"," improve"," the"," overall"," system"," efficiency"," and"," utilization","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-70b","label":1}